node.text:
I made my own 'Pretty Little Wishlist' on @nate_app with things that I'm loving right now. We're going to gift two people any item from my list in hopes that we can #MakeSomeoneSmile. @adwarren @iamtydavis 

To enter the contest:

(1) download the app and follow @nate_app

(2) follow my Pretty Little Gift Guide (link in bio) 

(3) comment below your favorite item + tag three friends.  

#NatePartner

Per Instagram rules, I must mention this giveaway is in no way sponsored, administered, or associated with Instagram inc. By entering, entrants confirm they are 18+ years of age, release instagram of responsibility, and agree to instagram terms of use.

node.title: The Holidays might be over but that doesn’t mean the gifting needs to stop!

node.text: This summer, I'm loving the Happy Limited Edition Collection by @hempzofficial (25% off all orders for a limited time with my code Ashley25!) It’s time for some good vibes after the past year and a half, and the Sweet Pineapple & Honey Melon Scent transports you to a tropical paradise 🏝 Hydration is key with the summer months getting hotter and hotter, which is why I always stick with Hempz products because the 100% Hemp Seed Oil always delivers on moisturization. They also made the scent available as a candle, so even staying home feels like a vacation.
